summary: But imagine how much sadder THAT scene will be if Snubbull's there too.  You'll have the audience bawling!
question: But imagine how much sadder THAT scene will be if Snubbull's there too.  You'll have the audience bawling!
answer:
I would prefer Snubbull staying in the submarine, watching the screens and hearing from a speaker or something. I can’t imagine him taking Snubull with him.

Oh god, what if his last line was actually directed at Snubbull? And then we cut back to him all upset?

Oh no.
